{"synckey":1653423730,"updated":[{"bookId":"839632","bookmarkId":"839632_6_5272-5313","chapterUid":6,"markText":"一个超级品牌就是一个伟大的符号系统。品牌要么始于符号，要么成为符号，通常两者都是。","range":"5272-5313","createTime":1653423730,"type":1},{"bookId":"839632","bookmarkId":"839632_6_777-902","chapterUid":6,"markText":"超级符号是人们本来就记得、熟悉、喜欢的符号，并且还会听它的指挥；超级符号是蕴藏在人类文化里的“原力”，是隐藏在人类大脑深处的集体潜意识。它已经为掌握引爆它引信的人积聚了数万年的能量，将超级符号嫁接给品牌，就得到超级创意、超级产品、超级品牌、超级企业。","range":"777-902","createTime":1653423568,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"什么是超级符号？","chapterUid":6,"chapterIdx":6}],"book":{"bookId":"839632","version":120272282,"format":"epub","soldout":1,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/47/YueWen_839632/s_YueWen_839632.jpg","title":"超级符号就是超级创意：席卷中国市场14年的华与华战略营销创意方法（全彩增订版）","author":"华杉 华楠","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KpMPZ$WX-m~4bba#9vWYWD","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#2d1800"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#331500"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#391200"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#402e07"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#462c00"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#4a2a00"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#59451f"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#5e4301"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#624200"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#693f00"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#795c1b"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#805900"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#735d33"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#9d7300"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#8e764b"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#9a740f"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#a89163"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#b08f4a"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#b68e2d"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#bd8c00"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#d1a848"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#d7a725"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#dba600"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#ddc694"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#e5c47b"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#f8c011"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#efe2c5"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#ffdc36"},{"key":"1/100","hex":"#b68e2d"},{"key":"2/100","hex":"#d1a848"},{"key":"3/100","hex":"#ffffff"},{"key":"4/100","hex":"#F3F1E5"},{"key":"5/100","hex":"#F3F1E5"},{"key":"6/100","hex":"#271E00"}],"dominate_color":{"hex":"#f9c32a","hsv":[44.53565857846,83.2596946991357,97.47001215945316]},"custom_cover":"h